  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, W-SI-01)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile and carries a hash but no digital signature, leaving structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01). All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels under the Minimal profile acceptance threshold. Decision: Accepted.",
